title: Living Bomb
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

[[Spore Mine]] Clusters are non-scoring, non-denial units. They do not award Victory Points when destroyed, and Wounds suffered by [[Spore Mine]]s in close combat (including those caused by a [[Floating Death]] detonation) are not counted when determining assault results.